{2: '???', 3: 'How is it, adapting to the new environment well?'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Yes, it's all good. You don't have to worry.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Not to mention, you should know exactly how I'm doing, shouldn't you?", 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Haha, you could say so.'}
{2: '???', 3: "But, I'd feel more relieved hearing it from you directly."}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Don't worry so much about me. It'll get to me as well.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Have more faith in both yourself and me.', 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Just, seeing you with that commandant...'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Makes me a bit jealous.'}
{2: '???', 3: "If I could, I'd like to go to Earth with you too..."}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Don't be silly... The commandant is in constant danger of consciousness damage and death just being on a mission.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'It might seem noble and exciting, but if I can...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "I'd like for you to live safe and sound. Just that.", 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: "I'm all grown up now, unlike before!"}
{2: '???', 3: "I've been working hard to catch up to you..."}
{2: '???', 3: 'Binary is nothing but a piece of cake to me now!'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Right, right, but you still have a long way to go if you want to surpass me.', 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: "Tch, I'll get there someday!"}
{2: '???', 3: "And then I'll be the one protecting you..."}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'All grown up, huh...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Alright then. I look forward to that day.', 4: '1'}
